response.original_title: Dash Cole: The Opal Card Story
response.overview: Avery is stuck at the gates in Central Station, and is trying to scan their Opal Card for entry, but it keeps declining. She asks security what to do but they are of no help. She then mentions that she wants to catch a train, and the security woman transforms into Dash Cole. Dash heard them say the word "train" and immediately jumps to the rescue to buy them a new Opal Card.
response.title: Dash Cole: The Opal Card Story
